{"div":{"@":{"xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","type":"article","xml:id":"MG-1699-01_279","resp":"wordpro"},"#":[{"head":{"value":"[Nouveaux Bouts-rimez des Lanternistes de Toulouse]","id":"/div/#[0]/head"}},{"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure Galant","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", janvier 1699 [tome 1] p. 279-281.","id":"/div/#[1]/bibl/#"}}},{"p":{"#1":{"value":"L’Académie de M","id":"/div/#[2]/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"rs","id":"/div/#[2]/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":". les Lanternistes de Toulouse, a proposé de nouveaux Bouts rimez à la gloire du Roy. Ces Bouts rimez sont","id":"/div/#[2]/p/#2"}}},{"table":{"row":[{"cell":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Temple.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[0]/cell[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ample.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[0]/cell[1]/hi/#"}}}]},{"cell":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cours.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[1]/cell[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jours.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[1]/cell[1]/hi/#"}}}]},{"cell":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Secours.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[2]/cell[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Amours.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[2]/cell[1]/hi/#"}}}]},{"cell":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Contemple.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[3]/cell[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Exemple.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[3]/cell[1]/hi/#"}}}]},{"cell":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Bataillons.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[4]/cell[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pouvoir.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[4]/cell[1]/hi/#"}}}]},{"cell":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sillons.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[5]/cell[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Declare.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[5]/cell[1]/hi/#"}}}]},{"cell":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Repare.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[6]/cell[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Espoir.","id":"/div/#[3]/table/row[6]/cell[1]/hi/#"}}}]}]}},{"p":{"#1":{"value":"Les Sonnets seront toûjours accompagnez d’une Priere en quatre Vers pour le Roy, &amp; d’une Sentence. Les Auteurs mettront leur Seing couvert &amp; cacheté au bas de leurs Sonnets, ou dans une Lettre séparée, le tout sous la mesme enveloppe &amp; rendu franc de port chez M","id":"/div/#[4]/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/#[4]/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":". Seré, prés la Place de Roaix à Toulouse, huit Jours avant la S. Jean. On avertit que les Sonnets qui seront en petits vers ou à rimes composées, ne pourront prétendre au Prix. On veut des Vers Alexandrins Heroïques, comme plus propres à la dignité du Sujet.","id":"/div/#[4]/p/#2"}}}]}}